uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.motor

Class IRelaxedInstantiator

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.motor.IRelaxedInstantiator

  • public abstract class IRelaxedInstantiator
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for regenerating previously existing instance-level frame/slot networks, without performing the normal reasoning operations that would be required if the networks were being built up from scratch. Specifically suitable for regenerating networks that have been serialised in some way. Enables the generation of either normal instances or "free-instances" (see IFreeCopier).
